  derThin (chk {R} rule Ts ts dz)     th Th
    rewrite plugThinLemma (chkInp R) Ts th | plugThinLemma (chkSuj R) ts th
    = let dz' , _ , _ = premsThin (chkPrems R) [] Ts ts dz th Th in 
