  derThin {ga} (elir {R} rule e Ss ss d dz) {de}{De} th Th
    with elir rule (e ^ th) (Ss ^E th) (ss ^E th) | derThin d th Th
  ... | ready | d'
    with premises ga (elimPrems R) ([] -, e) Ss ss
